  "detailed_description": "<h1>Play my New Game! - CONQUER HUMANITY</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Join our Community here<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Physics Based Battles.</strong></h2>Filled with funny ragdoll moments and dismemberments that you rarely see in games!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527910/extras/1fbd2c27268560962bd0e12b0aaf6625.poster.avif?t=1670421080\" width=720 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527910/extras/1fbd2c27268560962bd0e12b0aaf6625.webm?t=1670421080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527910/extras/1fbd2c27268560962bd0e12b0aaf6625.mp4?t=1670421080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527910/extras/1f16611be9e7624dbb0b469ea6ed222a.webp?t=1670421080\" width=618 height=21 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fight in Big Brawls.</strong></h2>Simulate large battles in teams or free for all, why not trying a 1 v 50!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527910/extras/50edd10d708827ea5a9fafbaba262be2.poster.avif?t=1670421080\" width=720 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527910/extras/50edd10d708827ea5a9fafbaba262be2.webm?t=1670421080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527910/extras/50edd10d708827ea5a9fafbaba262be2.mp4?t=1670421080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527910/extras/1f16611be9e7624dbb0b469ea6ed222a.webp?t=1670421080\" width=618 height=21 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Use the Environment and Traps.</strong></h2>Grab and Push opponents on traps or use your swings and momentum to deliver lethal hits!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527910/extras/ce50d9dba860cf82423c614ded1b727d.poster.avif?t=1670421080\" width=712 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527910/extras/ce50d9dba860cf82423c614ded1b727d.webm?t=1670421080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527910/extras/ce50d9dba860cf82423c614ded1b727d.mp4?t=1670421080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527910/extras/1f16611be9e7624dbb0b469ea6ed222a.webp?t=1670421080\" width=618 height=21 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fight Bosses and Unique Enemies.</strong></h2>It's not just about spamming attacks... be tactical, dodge and catch your enemies off-guard!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527910/extras/6404a28945872553cfc78aeaa1bdcc1d.poster.avif?t=1670421080\" width=720 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527910/extras/6404a28945872553cfc78aeaa1bdcc1d.webm?t=1670421080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527910/extras/6404a28945872553cfc78aeaa1bdcc1d.mp4?t=1670421080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527910/extras/1f16611be9e7624dbb0b469ea6ed222a.webp?t=1670421080\" width=618 height=21 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WARNING:</strong> You thought you were good at games ? Think twice, this is actually difficult.</h2>If you're skilled, you can execute in one hit and so can your opponents as-well. Misjudging a fight or not reacting fast enough can result in your head spinning away from your body, losing the Glory you've collected and starting all over again.",
